個星期，有投票權的人包括購買了AKB48單曲的人、AKB48歌迷會會員等「AKB的消費者」，即是說投票權是與金錢消費掛扣，一人是可以投超過一票"},{"pid":"040ccbaa14254bd8019504a20c687946b402923b","tid":1749407,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"日豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be21c9cbf728687a89eccfcdf64a43414183675","tid":1749407,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"平和一之棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16125a6740daa6aa403e5dcbc2223be8044510b","tid":1749407,"uid":107231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"啱啱出冊？<br />\n神7有人做埋阿媽啦"},{"pid":"1b2b877451c0901affdd931fda244bc9447580d9","tid":1749407,"uid":180975,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"日本試下政客偶像化應該有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30e81318942c42119603c6eb259af93eede7d6d","tid":1749407,"uid":18309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"All ugly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6e10a1f2130550b2cc8e2bad9f6e1c234a79e9","tid":1749407,"uid":84926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d2d96d5120e9b86f3082668bdb70a3fc3a0520b","tid":1749407,"uid":184726,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"佢地嘅民主係美國送比佢地<br />\n講奴性佢地比支那有過之而無不及"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"但人地日本人應該真愛國<br />\n支那奴得黎唔愛國專害鳩自己人<br />\n毒奶粉 豆腐渣樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b6aa1d826087737a1e73251fa1814c1b3aa754","tid":1749407,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"日本其實仲慘<br />\n老人太多<br />\n而家香港年青人仲叫做有得揀下<br />\n佢地係無<br />\n全部都只係服務老人<br />\n<br />\n香港遲早都會<br />\n我地得返好少時間"},{"pid":"01102d